These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | reading |
| Cigar       | game | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, collecting
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Hobby   | board-games | collecting |
| Color      | coral     | blood-red  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, journalist
1. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | ice-hockey  |
| Job   | project-manager | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, zombie
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | poppy   |
| Movie-Genre       | zombie | spy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
2 different games are played: poker, backgammon
2 different pets are kept: goat, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Game   | backgammon    | poker    |
| Pet   | goat | bird |

 #################################

 
