.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-9::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, polish
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, april
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the polish##1
2. the colombian is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian  |
| Birthday       | april   | september |

